# midisim
## Calculate, search, and analyze MIDI-to-MIDI similarity at scale

<img width="1536" height="1024" alt="midisim" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/0b379b3a-ec9f-42c7-ba09-6b7cce87a338" />

